snippet.textDisplay:
Hi Yes Theory! My name is Katie Barraco and I’m an 18 year old college student. I love u guys so much. Yes theory has helped me get out of my darkest times and I don’t know where I would be without you guys. You live a life I have always wanted to live and you guys give me faith. I got an opportunity by Beyond Sports to go do what I love (play soccer) in Costa Rica. It has been my dream since I was 2 years old to go to the next level and I finally have the chance. I will be playing the top 3 teams and coaching kids while there. I want to be able to show my love for the game to the world and kids and be able to make a difference. My first thought was I don’t think I could go on my own with my anxiety but then I thought of u guys and said what would yes theory do....”seek discomfort.” This could change my life but I unfortunately do not have the money to make it there. It cost $2495 dollars to go. I need $1000 by December 27th for a down payment and the rest can be paid later. I am not asking at any means to pay for it but if possible make a donation to my gofundme. Anything helps no matter how small!
https://www.gofundme.com/f/mvygz-beyond-sports-tour?utm_source=customer&utm_medium=sms&utm_campaign=p_cf+share-flow-1
